Currently, the following message types are defined: PKCSReq (19) -- Permits use of PKCS#10 certificate request CertRep (3) -- Response to certificate or CRL request GetCertInitial (20) -- Certificate polling in manual enrollment GetCert (21) -- Retrieve a certificate GetCRL (22) -- Retrieve a CRL
